{"id": "1228597068533075979", "channel_id": "1228565524850675764", "type": 0, "author_id": "485414453152841749", "author_name": "wodebaobaoxiaodangaovi", "author_bot": false, "content": "艾爾瓦，盾擊玩法十分穩定卻並不泛用。融災禁區，主線H6-10(黑潮)只剩半盾，深潛又很難提速，經過反擊造物大砍，失去低成本盾反隊，3啟後又處處受限。所以是B", "timestamp": "2024-04-13T06:46:07.368000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1228565524850675764", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "混沌節奏雙榜", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179680056791130", "1174179700470460447"]}
{"id": "1228597286926422068", "channel_id": "1228565524850675764", "type": 0, "author_id": "485414453152841749", "author_name": "wodebaobaoxiaodangaovi", "author_bot": false, "content": "朵爾挺強，但是寄人籬下需要跟其他界別的怪物輔助搶位置，搶不過別人就只能是B。", "timestamp": "2024-04-13T06:46:59.437000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1228565524850675764", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "混沌節奏雙榜", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179680056791130", "1174179700470460447"]}
